laboratory_examinations.findings: A missense mutation, Arg531Gly, was identified in all affected individuals but was absent in 150 unrelated individuals.
Normal left ventricular (LV) function, interventricular septal thickness of 9 mm, and maximal LV free wall thickness of 11 mm.
